    "description": "<p><strong>YTL CE And Builder Pte Ltd</strong>&nbsp;was incorporated in 2015, was formed by an experienced team specialized in civil engineering works.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The Company is registered with the Building and Construction Authority of Singapore (BCA) under the following workheads:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>CW02 – Civil Engineering (Grade C3)</li>\n  <li>CR07 - Grade L5</li>\n  <li>GB License – General Builder Class 1</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We are actively looking for opportunities to establish mutual beneficial business relationship with reputable and prestigious companies that would push the boundaries and break the barriers of the local construction scene.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Our Company Slogan</strong></p>\n<p>1. Together we can achieve greatness.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Our Mission Statement</strong></p>\n<p>1. &nbsp;We strive to deliver the best work quality to our clients</p>\n<p>2. &nbsp;Build and cultivate long term business relationship with clients</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><u><strong>Scope of Works and Services</strong></u></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>New underground water and sewer pipelines installation by open trench excavation method or trenchless deep excavation method (Pipe Jacking Method).</li>\n  <li>Other infrastructure works involve such as road and drainage construction.</li>\n</ul>",
